title: Arbor Snowboards :: Product Profiles - Draft
description:
From city parks to terrain parks, this jib-specific rocker is your go-to board when it comes to buttering that muffin, gapping the donkey, or back lipping the coping. Translation: The Draft is a jibbing machine.
To learn more about the Draft visit: arborcollective.com/snowboards/products/draft/
